title: DAZ3D - Poser - Kimberly Expressions, Poses and Clothing Texture
description:
Expressions:
Breath some life into your Kimberly for Genesis Character with this set of 25 expression morph dials. From a very subtle, nonchalant look to one of anger and shock, all these expressions are completely blendable giving you lots of options and versatility.


Poses:
Kimberly Poses is a set of carefree, fun and everyday style poses for 3D Universe's Kimberly character. Each pose has been carefully crafted and detailed to look great from any angle.

Although these poses have been designed specifically for Kimberly, they can be slightly tweaked to fit other Genesis characters.


Textures:
A varied collection of summer styles and colors that will make your female Genesis characters turn heads on the sand. These 33 materials work together to create a vibrant and colorful wardrobe for summer.
